{"type": "article", "id": 10110, "title": "Romain Jerome Pac-Man 腕表", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-28T07:24:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235535Sgb1iApQ7ZFMTOvP.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t临近儿童节，各家也纷纷推出了充满纯真的系列产品。Pac-Man 是上个世纪 80 年代在日本推出的电脑游戏，多年来深受大家喜爱。瑞士腕表品牌 Romain Jerome 为了纪念其 35 岁生日，特意推出 Pac-Man 二代腕表。新系列共包含五款表，上面搭配了 Pac-Man 经典造型，唤起所有粉丝内心的童真。这款表全球限量 20 只，将会在儿童节当天开始发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235534F48M7oYRGBNPC51p.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235534iMFIf1uLqbcCW0gn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.10166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}